  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1 \u0bae\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bc7\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0b9f\u0bc0\u0b9a\u0bb2\u0bcd, \u0bae\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0ba3\u0bc6\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0ba3\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Recovery of diesel and kerosene stored in Modhu Mawdiwem",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Police have recovered 550 liters of diesel and 258 liters of kerosene stored in a building near a petrol station in the Mavadivembu area in the Batticaloa Junction police division.",
        "Following a tip-off received by the CID, the BSP, in consultation with Senior Superintendent of Police Sukath Masinghe, has been appointed. Bandara-led police cordoned off a building near a petrol station in the area at around 04.00 pm yesterday.",
        "During the raid, 550 liters of diesel and 258 liters of kerosene were recovered from the barrels and one person was arrested and handed over to the Junction Police."
      ],
